code: /**  * @return The watch status  */ public WatchStatus getStatus() {     return status. }
@Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     status = in.readBoolean() ? new WatchStatus(in) : null. }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeBoolean(status != null).     if (status != null) {         status.writeTo(out).     } }
